data.title: 'High School Musical's Corbin Bleu Shares First Wedding Photo
data.meta_description: 'High School Musical's Corbin Bleu got married last weekend on Saturday, July 23, and the star just shared his first wedding photo on Instagram.
data.text:
No matter how many years go by and where they all end up, the cast of High School Musical will always have a special place in our hearts. From Zac Efron's continuous growth as an actor to Ashley Tisdale's dive into the cosmetics industry with her makeup line, the East High alums have gone on to do great things after the three-part series.

Out of all the stars, Corbin Bleu, a.k.a. Chad Danforth, made one of the biggest life-changing decisions recently, and it will give you all the feels. The actor upgraded from the cast's senior year prom and got married last weekend on Saturday (July 23) to his long-time girlfriend, actress Sasha Clements.

Instagram content

This content can also be viewed on the site it originates from.

The HSM star shared the first Instagram photo of their wedding today and it's picture perfect. Though it seems no one from the OG cast is returning to the upcoming HSM 4, it's great to see they're all doing so well. In case you're really craving a throwback, just peep over at Vanessa Hudgens and Ashley Tisdale's social media accounts, those two are glued together as if the movie never ended.
